<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The Joint node is used to build skeletons as part of the skinned mesh support in Qt 3D. A joint can be transformed by way of its scale, rotation and translation properties. Any mesh vertices that are bound to the joint will have their transformations updated accordingly.</db:para>
</db:section>
